{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, I am indeed going to talk about"},{"time":3000,"text":"the spaces men create for themselves,"},{"time":5000,"text":"but first I want to tell you why I'm here."},{"time":7000,"text":"I'm here for two reasons. These two guys"},{"time":9000,"text":"are my two sons Ford and Wren."},{"time":12000,"text":"When Ford was about three years old,"},{"time":14000,"text":"we shared a very small room together,"},{"time":16000,"text":"in a very small space."},{"time":18000,"text":"My office was on one half of the bedroom,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and his bedroom was on the other half."},{"time":22000,"text":"And you can imagine, if you're a writer,"},{"time":24000,"text":"that things would get really crowded around deadlines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"So when Wren was on the way,"},{"time":29000,"text":"I realized I needed to find a space of my own."},{"time":31000,"text":"There was no more space in the house. So I went out to the backyard,"},{"time":34000,"text":"and without any previous building experience,"},{"time":36000,"text":"and about 3,000 dollars and some"},{"time":38000,"text":"recycled materials, I built this space."},{"time":40000,"text":"It had everything I needed. It was quiet."},{"time":43000,"text":"There was enough space. And I had control, which was very important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"As I was building this space, I thought"},{"time":48000,"text":"to myself, \"Surely I'm not the only guy"},{"time":50000,"text":"to have to have carved out a space for his own.\""},{"time":53000,"text":"So I did some research."},{"time":55000,"text":"And I found that there was an historic precedence."},{"time":57000,"text":"Hemingway had his writing space."},{"time":59000,"text":"Elvis had two or three manspaces,"},{"time":61000,"text":"which is pretty unique because he lived with both his wife and his mother in Graceland."},{"time":65000,"text":"In the popular culture, Superman had the Fortress of Solitude,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and there was, of course, the Batcave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"So I realized then that I wanted to go out on a journey"},{"time":76000,"text":"and see what guys were creating for themselves now."},{"time":79000,"text":"Here is one of the first spaces I found. It is in Austin, Texas,"},{"time":81000,"text":"which is where I'm from."},{"time":83000,"text":"On the outside it looks like a very typical garage, a nice garage."},{"time":86000,"text":"But on the inside, it's anything but."},{"time":88000,"text":"And this, to me, is a pretty classic manspace."},{"time":90000,"text":"It has neon concert posters, a bar"},{"time":94000,"text":"and, of course, the leg lamp,"},{"time":96000,"text":"which is very important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"I soon realized that manspaces didn't have to be only inside."},{"time":101000,"text":"This guy built a bowling alley in his backyard,"},{"time":104000,"text":"out of landscaping timbers, astroturf."},{"time":106000,"text":"And he found the scoreboard in the trash."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"Here's another outdoor space, a little bit more sophisticated."},{"time":111000,"text":"This a 1923 wooden tugboat,"},{"time":114000,"text":"made completely out of Douglas fir."},{"time":116000,"text":"The guy did it all himself."},{"time":118000,"text":"And there is about 1,000 square feet of hanging-out space inside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"So, pretty early on in my investigations"},{"time":125000,"text":"I realized what I was finding was not what I expected to find,"},{"time":128000,"text":"which was, quite frankly, a lot of beer can pyramids"},{"time":130000,"text":"and overstuffed couches and flat-screen TVs."},{"time":133000,"text":"There were definitely hang-out spots."},{"time":135000,"text":"But some were for working, some were for playing,"},{"time":138000,"text":"some were for guys to collect their things."},{"time":141000,"text":"Most of all, I was just surprised with what I was finding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"Take this place for example."},{"time":146000,"text":"On the outside it looks like a typical northeastern garage."},{"time":148000,"text":"This is in Long Island, New York."},{"time":150000,"text":"The only thing that might tip you off is the round window."},{"time":153000,"text":"On the inside it's a recreation of a"},{"time":155000,"text":"16th century Japanese tea house."},{"time":158000,"text":"The man imported all the materials from Japan,"},{"time":160000,"text":"and he hired a Japanese carpenter"},{"time":163000,"text":"to build it in the traditional style."},{"time":165000,"text":"It has no nails or screws."},{"time":167000,"text":"All the joints are hand-carved and hand-scribed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"Here is another pretty typical scene. This is a suburban Las Vegas neighborhood."},{"time":173000,"text":"But you open one of the garage doors"},{"time":176000,"text":"and there is a professional-size boxing ring inside."},{"time":179000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":180000,"text":"And so there is a good reason for this."},{"time":182000,"text":"It was built by this man who is Wayne McCullough."},{"time":184000,"text":"He won the silver medal for Ireland"},{"time":186000,"text":"in the 1992 Olympics,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and he trains in this space. He trains other people."},{"time":191000,"text":"And right off the garage he has his own trophy room"},{"time":194000,"text":"where he can sort of bask in his accomplishments,"},{"time":196000,"text":"which is another sort of important part about a manspace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199000,"text":"So, while this space represents someone's profession,"},{"time":202000,"text":"this one certainly represents a passion."},{"time":204000,"text":"It's made to look like the inside of an English sailing ship."},{"time":207000,"text":"It's a collection of nautical antiques from the 1700s and 1800s."},{"time":210000,"text":"Museum quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212000,"text":"So, as I came to the end of my journey,"},{"time":214000,"text":"I found over 50 spaces."},{"time":216000,"text":"And they were unexpected and they were surprising."},{"time":218000,"text":"But they were also --"},{"time":220000,"text":"I was really impressed by how personalized they were,"},{"time":222000,"text":"and how much work went into them."},{"time":224000,"text":"And I realized that's because the guys that I met"},{"time":226000,"text":"were all very passionate about what they did."},{"time":228000,"text":"And they really loved their professions."},{"time":230000,"text":"And they were very passionate about their collections and their hobbies."},{"time":232000,"text":"And so they created these spaces"},{"time":234000,"text":"to reflect what they love to do,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and who they were."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"So if you don't have a space of your own,"},{"time":241000,"text":"I highly recommend finding one, and getting into it."},{"time":243000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":245000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}